- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 of 6 static patterns (with proper `#if` fallback)
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` and `WordCount` use efficient `foreach` loops
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `ToLowerInvariant()` correctly
- ✅ `Dasherize` uses `char` overload of `Replace` (no regex overhead)

